  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A continental breakfast is served each morning and includes a wide selection of breads, cheeses, cold cuts, cereals and hot options like eggs and bacon. The coffee is made to order and there's a good selection of tea's to choose from. You can have it either in the breakfast room or outside on the terrace overlooking the valley.</p>
<p><strong>The Collins Restaurant </strong>is known for its regional and fresh produce dishes full of Umbrian flavours. Enjoy lunch and/or dinner here with a panoramic view. In the warmer months you can sit outside on the rooftop terrace and on cooler days, dinner can be enjoyed inside in the cosy restaurant in front of the roaring fire. Don't for get to have a look at the extensive wine list where you'll have a choice of the best Italian wines. Try the local ones for the best authentic experience. </p>
<p><strong>Collins Bar</strong> is the place to go for cocktails or afternoon tea. In the summer you can sit out on the terrace and watch the fashionable locals walking by the promenade. </p>
<p><strong>Bar Bellavista </strong>is open during the cooler months. Inside it has large windows overlooking the Umbrian valley. Its a nice spot to sit with a hot chocolate or even a glass of local red. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
