  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>The wellness area is located in the medieval vaults beneath the hotel. The pool has a transparent bottom that looks down into the ruins of an Etruscan settlement that dates back 3000 years - so its a pretty special place for a swim. There's a sauna, Turkish bath and relaxation area down here too - so its easy to relax down here in this tranquil setting. There are in-room Spa massages and treatments on request, which you can book and pay for locally. </p>
<p>Opening times: 7am - 10pm </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Panoramic Terrace </li>
<li>Free WiFi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
