  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are furnished in a classic and elegant style with lots of character. They sleep up to two people are are around 30m². Rooms are fully equipped with air conditioning, TV, telephone, safe, minibar, bathrobes and slippers. </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are approximately 40m² and have been furnished with antique furniture. They have unforgettable views over the Umbrian Valley. These rooms sleep up to three people. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are spacious at approximately 47m² and sleep up to three people. These rooms are decorated with antique furniture and have a lounge area. </p>
<p><strong>Suites </strong>are very spacious at about 52m² and sleep up to three people. These rooms have inner courtyard or valley views. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>Superior and Deluxe rooms are available for single use. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
